&control
    calculation = 'nscf'
    prefix = 'mos2monorel'
    outdir = './mos2monorel/'
    pseudo_dir = './pseudos/'
    verbosity = 'high'
/

&system
    ibrav=0,
    nat=3,
    ntyp=2,
    ecutwfc=40,
    ecutrho=400,
    occupations='fixed',
    nbnd=80,
    noncolin= .true.,
    lspinorb= .true.

/

&electrons
    conv_thr=1.0d-8
    mixing_beta=0.3
    electron_maxstep=200
/

ATOMIC_SPECIES
Mo 95.95 Mo.UPF
S  32.06 S.UPF

CELL_PARAMETERS (angstrom)
3.1840   0.0000   0.0000
-1.5920  2.7574   0.0000
0.0000   0.0000   20.0

ATOMIC_POSITIONS (crystal)
Mo 0.3333319773 0.6666639546 0.0868542419
S  0.6666506829 0.3333013648 0.0017359946
S  0.6666506738 0.3333013466 0.1719722054

K_POINTS (automatic)
18 18 1 0 0 0